---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <CategoryHero
    title={title}
    description={description}
    image="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1532295454114-d7bc89024613"
  />

  <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-16">
      <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600">
        Peru's rich cultural heritage offers photographers a unique blend of ancient traditions and modern life.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6">Cultural Locations</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
      {photoSpots.map(spot => (
        <PhotoSpot {...spot} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Photography Tips</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      {photographyTips.map(tip => (
        <PhotoTip {...tip} />
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <h2>Essential Information</h2>
      <h3>Best Times to Visit</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>May to October (dry season)</li>
        <li>June for Inti Raymi festival</li>
        <li>Early morning for markets</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Equipment Recommendations</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Versatile zoom lens (24-70mm)</li>
        <li>Portrait lens (85mm)</li>
        <li>Polarizing filter</li>
        <li>Portable flash</li>
        <li>Weather-sealed gear</li>
      </ul>

      <blockquote>
        <p>"Peru's cultural heritage is a living museum, where ancient traditions blend seamlessly with modern life."</p>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>